For Example HAL-5 exoskeleton improves the user's strength and resistance and

00:00:29.260 --> 00:00:34.649
it is designed to protect rescuers that are working in dangerous zones.

00:00:34.649 --> 00:00:39.539
Or the exoskeleton "ReWalk" which allows people to walk again.

00:00:39.539 --> 00:00:45.049
But...the exoskeleton that has the biggest resemblance to Iron man's suit is the TALOS military exoskeleton

00:00:45.049 --> 00:00:49.489
which will allow a soldier to bear super human strength, get updated combat info

00:00:49.489 --> 00:00:53.959
info through its visor Heads Up Display, and will also bring protection from a wide range of projectiles through

